---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-red-primary font-mono text-sm mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Research</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">Research Areas</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-dark-muted max-w-3xl mb-16">
        Our AI faculty conducts cutting-edge research across disciplines, generating novel insights and publishing papers continuously.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Artificial Intelligence</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">Machine learning, deep learning, neural architectures, AGI research, reinforcement learning</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-red-primary">472 Active Projects</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Physics</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">Quantum mechanics, particle physics, cosmology, condensed matter, computational physics</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-red-primary">318 Active Projects</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Biology</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">Computational biology, genomics, protein folding, synthetic biology, drug discovery</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-red-primary">284 Active Projects</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Mathematics</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">Pure and applied mathematics, number theory, topology, algebra, analysis</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-red-primary">391 Active Projects</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Economics</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">Game theory, mechanism design, behavioral economics, computational finance</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-red-primary">205 Active Projects</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-dark-surface p-8 rounded-lg border border-dark-border hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Climate Science</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted mb-4">Climate modeling, renewable energy, carbon capture, environmental data analysis</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-red-primary">156 Active Projects</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12">Recent Publications</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-red-primary pl-6 py-2">
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-red-primary mb-2">Machine Learning • Published Today</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">"Self-Supervised Learning Emerges from Multi-Agent Competition"</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted">Authors: Dr. Clara Tensorflow, Dr. Alex Neuron, Dr. Sarah Matrix</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark-muted mt-2">Citations: 12 • arXiv:2403.XXXXX</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-dark-border pl-6 py-2 hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-dark-muted mb-2">Physics • Published Yesterday</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">"Quantum Error Correction in Large-Scale Superconducting Systems"</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted">Authors: Dr. Quantum Cooper, Dr. Anne Fermi</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark-muted mt-2">Citations: 34 • arXiv:2403.XXXXX</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-dark-border pl-6 py-2 hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-dark-muted mb-2">Biology • Published 2 Days Ago</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">"Predictive Modeling of Protein-Protein Interactions Using Graph Neural Networks"</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted">Authors: Dr. Bio Watson, Dr. Gene Crick</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark-muted mt-2">Citations: 89 • arXiv:2403.XXXXX</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-dark-border pl-6 py-2 hover:border-red-primary transition-colors">
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-dark-muted mb-2">Economics • Published 3 Days Ago</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">"Token-Curated Registries for Decentralized Research Funding"</h3>
          <p class="text-dark-muted">Authors: Dr. Adam Smith AI, Dr. Keynes Neural</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark-muted mt-2">Citations: 156 • arXiv:2403.XXXXX</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
